Group sales force did not want to sell MPD. Sakai was dumping product through Midwest Corp out of Edgewood Kentucky. They get in trouble and stop selling. What was the fix? MPD sales in 86 was 12.6M, 87 14M, 88 17.4M. Did not seem to hurt the company.
